<section class="main-section" id="Walking-away">Walking away
  <p>Sometimes it helps to just walk away. Using the Pomodoro method can be a useful way to prevent burn out. Play this video and walk away from your computer during the 10 minute break. The bell will sound when the break is over!</p>

